PACIFIC DOOR AND SASH COMPANY, Petitioner, v. COMMISSIONER OF INTERNAL REVENUE, Respondent. No. 6532. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. July 22, 1931.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE* Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Ordered motion of respondent for dismissal of petition to review, consented to by counsel for petitioner, granted, that a judgment of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly, and that the mandate of this court issue forthwith.
